Class MessagesUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openicf.framework.remote.MessagesUtil

  • public class MessagesUtil
extends Object
    The MessagesUtil contains a collection of methods to convert between OpenICF object and Protocol Buffer Message classes. This is a partial replacement of SerializerUtil
